Compute the ending point of the provided line segment along the 'x' axis.



```js
segEndX(tag: TagIdentifier) -> number
```

### Examples

```js
const exampleSketch = startSketchOn('XZ')
  |> startProfileAt([0, 0], %)
  |> line([20, 0], %, $thing)
  |> line([0, 5], %)
  |> line([segEndX(thing), 0], %)
  |> line([-20, 10], %)
  |> close(%)

const example = extrude(5, exampleSketch)
```
